        this.addCustomerChat(CommonCustomersChat.KAPPA_CHAT_0, "", "哦？原来也有这种店面啊。");
        this.addCustomerChat(CommonCustomersChat.KAPPA_CHAT_1, "", "没有学过的菜谱就算强行做出来也会奇奇怪怪的，还是循序渐进的好。");
